text: Harish Marotiappa Pimple is a member of the 13th Maharashtra Legislative Assembly. He represents the Murtizapur Assembly Constituency. He belongs to the Bharatiya Janata Party. ==References== Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Living people Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Maharashtra Category:People from Akola district Category:Marathi politicians Category:1964 births Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2019–
